news_header: Romania charges Andrew Tate with trafficking and sexual offences.
news_original_title: Lehti: USA painostaa Romaniaa poistamaan Andrew Taten matkustus­rajoitukset
news_text: Romania has charged Andrew Tate and his brother with human trafficking, sexual offences, and money laundering, amid US pressure to lift travel restrictions on Tate. The brothers are dual citizens and cannot leave Romania during the trial.
